WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Agent: Ada, Minh — thanks for joining. Let's start with the two pilot deployments. What changed between the first and the second?

00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:22.000
Ada Example: The first took nine days on site. We rebuilt the demonstration capture flow, and the second was live in under two days.

00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:30.000
Agent: Your deck states $120K ARR, but the application says $80K. Help me reconcile those.

00:00:30.500 --> 00:00:45.000
Minh Example: The $120K includes the second pilot that's signed but starts billing next quarter. Contracted today is $80K ARR.

00:00:45.500 --> 00:00:58.000
Ada Example: We founded the company in 2025 after we both worked at Fraunhofer on manipulation research. We interviewed 60 warehouse operators before writing code.

00:00:58.500 --> 00:01:10.000
Minh Example: Honestly, the founding was 2026 on paper — we incorporated later than we started building. We raised $250K from angels to get the first robot arm.
